    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a hardship because of the way I was being treated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the war was over, I kept hoping that my parents would come, and I would go back and have my life the way it used to be before the war, which never happened.",
